replies.body:
I am bumping this thread because, this issue is STILL rampant. This has been happening to me for at least 2 months now, and I have tried everything. Just last night I had to factory restore my PC due to this bug, then I play other games all day long and I don't get so much as a hiccup, but as SOON as I log into League, my entire machine seizes up and then I get the classic BSOD ":( Oops..." 

This has made it nearly impossible to play my favorite game. {{champion:32}}

I'd at least like to know Riot is aware of this issue, its affecting a lot of people.
